title: Plato (E-Books and Articles)
description:
Here are my e-books (all PDFs, most of high quality, some, however, are scanned images of books) and articles by or about Plato and his philosophy:

Cambridge Companion to Plato
Chorology - John Sallis
Knowing Persons, A Study in Plato - Lloyd Gerson
Opera - John Burnet
Philosophy Guidebook to Plato and the Trail of Socrates
Symposium - [CUP]
Plato's Theory of Eikasia
Platonis Opera
Platonism
Plato's Introduction of Forms - [CUP]
Lysis - [CUP]
Plato's Meno [CUP]
Plato's Phaedo - Burnet
Plato's Phaedo with critical notes and analysis
Plato's Republic
Commentary on the Timaeus I - Proclus
Commentary on the Timaeus II - Proclus
Plato - Robert Hall
Plato's Parmenides - Samuel Sclnicov
Text and Interpretation of Philebus 56a
The Birth of Rhetoric
The Phaedrus of Plato
The Philebus of Plato
The Role of The Hypothetical Method in The Phaedo

There are an additional 18 scholarly articles included in this torrent
